    "Id": "chassisdef_valkyrie_ii_VLK-II-HLD",
    "Name": "Valkyrie II",
    "Details": "Despite the dark cloud of graft looming over the Valkyrie II project, the Steiner and Davion stables of Solaris VII quickly jumped at the opportunity to get their hands on the heavily armored and incredibly fast Valkyrie II chassis for retrofitting into gladiatorial designs. 'Hildr' is one such design fitted with a BattleMech Mace, capable of crushing armor and internal components in one blow, and a Snub-Nose PPC to finish off anything strong enough to be standing after its assaults. \n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Integrated TSM</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.08</color></b>",
